Hello! Welcome to Aquidneck Yacht Brokers customer support. My name is Scott Adams. How can I assist you today?

Hi Scott, I'm having an issue with a gift card I received.

I'm sorry to hear that, Michelle. Can you tell me more about the issue?

The gift card was for one hundred dollars, but when I tried to use it, it said it was invalid.

I see. Could I please have the gift card number to look into this for you?

Certainly, it's one two three four five six seven eight.

Thank you, Michelle. And may I also have the date you received the card?

I received it on September first.

Great, thank you. I'll check our system to see what might be the issue.

Alright, I've resolved the problem. Your card is now activated and ready to use. Thank you for your patience, Michelle.

Thanks for your help, Scott. I appreciate it.

You're welcome, Michelle! Thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a great day!
